Created attachment 24806
Documentation/comment spelling fixes

The attached patch against current svn trunk contains a bunch of spelling fixes to docs and comments (negotation->negotiation, choosen->chosen, Engeschall->Engelschall, derivate->derivative, neccessary->necessary, a SSL->an SSL, successfull->successful).
Moving docs bugs to docs@httpd.a.o ownership.
